### Canonical Metadata and Units

All objects carry OSDU-aligned metadata via RESQML ExtraMetadata:

| ExtraMetadata Key | Value | OSDU Equivalent |
|---|---|---|
| `osdu:FieldName` | Drogon | `data.FieldNames[]` |
| `osdu:Basin` | Norwegian Continental Shelf | `data.BasinNames[]` |
| `osdu:DataSource` | Drogon Demo (Equinor) | `data.Source` |
| `osdu:HorizonName` | TopVolantis, etc. | `data.HorizonName` |

**Units of Measure (UOM)** – Energistics standard abbreviations:

| UOM | Meaning | Used By |
|---|---|---|
| `v/v` | Volume fraction (dimensionless) | Porosity, saturation, NTG, shale volume |
| `m3` | Cubic metres | Pore volume, bulk volume |
| `m` | Metres | CRS, depths, well MD |
| `mD` | Millidarcy | Permeability |
| `degC` | Degrees Celsius | Temperature |
| `dega` | Degrees (angle) | CRS areal rotation |
| `Euc` | Dimensionless (Euclidean) | Facies index, zone index |
| `m/s` | Metres per second | P-wave, S-wave velocity |
| `kg/m3` | Kilograms per cubic metre | Bulk density |
| `Pa` | Pascals (stress) | Acoustic/shear impedance |

**CRS** – Both depth and time systems defined:

| CRS Object | Projected | Vertical | Z Convention |
|---|---|---|---|
| LocalDepth3dCrs | ED50 / UTM 37S (m) | MSL (m) | Z increasing downward |
| LocalTime3dCrs | ED50 / UTM 37S (m) | TWT (ms) | Z increasing downward |

### Relationship Preservation

The EPC maintains the full RESQML relationship graph via OPC `.rels` files
and inline `DataObjectReference` elements:

```
Feature ←─── Interpretation ←─── Representation ←─── Property
   │                │                    │                │
   │                │                    ├── LocalCrs     ├── SupportingRep
   │                │                    └── HdfProxy     └── HdfProxy
   │                │
   │                └── InterpretedFeature (back-ref to Feature)
   │
   └── (GeneticBoundary / TectonicBoundary / StratigraphicUnit)
```

**Key relationships preserved in this archive:**

| From | Relationship | To |
|---|---|---|
| HorizonInterpretation | InterpretedFeature | GeneticBoundaryFeature |
| FaultInterpretation | InterpretedFeature | TectonicBoundaryFeature |
| StructuralOrganizationInterpretation | InterpretedFeature | OrganizationFeature |
| StructuralOrganizationInterpretation | Horizons[] | HorizonInterpretation (×6) |
| StructuralOrganizationInterpretation | Faults[] | FaultInterpretation (×6) |
| Grid2dRepresentation | RepresentedInterpretation | HorizonInterpretation |
| PointSetRepresentation | RepresentedInterpretation | Horizon/FaultInterpretation |
| PolylineSetRepresentation | RepresentedInterpretation | FaultInterpretation |
| IjkGridRepresentation | StratigraphicOrganization | StratigraphicColumnRankInterpretation |
| StratigraphicColumn | Ranks | StratigraphicColumnRankInterpretation |
| StratigraphicColumnRank | StratigraphicUnits | StratigraphicUnitInterpretation |
| StratigraphicUnitInterpretation | InterpretedFeature | StratigraphicUnitFeature |
| ContinuousProperty | SupportingRepresentation | IjkGrid / WellboreFrame |
| WellboreTrajectory | MdDatum | MdDatum |
| WellboreInterpretation | InterpretedFeature | WellboreFeature |
| All representations | LocalCrs | LocalDepth3dCrs / LocalTime3dCrs |
| All array holders | HdfProxy | EpcExternalPartReference |

