| | StratigraphicColumnRankInterpretation:1.3.0 | 1 |
| | LocalModelFeature:1.2.0 | 1 |

**Cross-references populated:**

| Reference Type | Count | Example |
|---|---|---|
| InterpretedFeature/BoundaryFeature | 46 | FaultInterpretation → LocalBoundaryFeature |
| CoordinateReferenceSystemID | 41 | StructureMap → LocalModelCompoundCrs |
| SupportingRepresentationID | 32 | GenericProperty → IjkGridRepresentation |
| WellboreID | 30 | WellLog/Trajectory/Markers → Wellbore |
